gov.nasa.jpf.util

Class SparseIntVector

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.jpf.util.SparseIntVector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable

    public class SparseIntVector
extends Object
implements Cloneable
    This has approximately the interface of IntVector but uses a hash table instead of an array. Also, does not require allocation with each add. Configurable default value.
